&lt;li&gt;Review executed loan documents for compliance with company, investor, agency, and regulatory requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Audit closed loan packages to identify missing documentation, document discrepancies, signature deficiencies, and data inconsistencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with Closing, Processing, Underwriting, Account Management, and external settlement partners to obtain required corrections and trailing documents&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage post-closing conditions and clear outstanding deficiencies in a timely manner&lt;/li&gt;
